Where the Gathering will be in 2002;

This year the North American Rainbow Gathering 
(hence referred to as the Gathering) will be in 
Michigan near the town of Watersmeet in Ottawa 
National Forest, from July 1 - July 7.

Directions:
 From Watersmeet, Michigan go about 5 miles north 
to a sign for "Robbin's Pond Campground". Turn 
left. Go about 1/2 mile to the 1st left onto FS 
2530. Drive down FS 2530 about 4-5 miles to the 
parking lot. Welcome Home!

Ignore all rumors of cancellation or 
organization! Live Lightly with the Land and 
People!


